business_context: The business specializes in food ordering and delivery services, connecting customers with various food providers.

suggested_features.name: Order Tracking
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to track the status of their food orders in real-time.

suggested_features.name: Delivery Scheduling
suggested_features.description: Enables customers to schedule delivery times for their orders.

suggested_features.name: Menu Customization
suggested_features.description: Provides options for customers to customize their orders with specific instructions.

suggested_features.name: Restaurant Reviews
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to leave and read reviews of restaurants and food providers.

suggested_features.name: Customer Support Chat
suggested_features.description: Offers live chat support for customers to resolve issues or inquiries quickly.

suggested_features.name: Order History
suggested_features.description: Allows customers to view and reorder past orders easily.
